A tragic incident unfolded in Glendale as a man parked his SUV on train tracks, causing a deadly collision involving multiple trains.
The chaos resulted in at least 10 fatalities and over 180 injuries.
The suspect, Juan Manuel Alvarez, faced murder charges for his intentional actions.
Witnesses described a scene of horror and heroism as passengers helped each other amidst the wreckage.
Emergency responders and firefighters worked tirelessly to rescue those trapped.
The community rallied together in the face of this devastating event, with many expressing shock and disbelief at the senseless loss of life.
